message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as it deals with sound and audio processing. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses neural networks for sound event detection, cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper involves feature extraction and analysis, cs.SI (signal processing) as it deals with audio signal processing, and cs.CL (computational linguistics) as sound event detection can be considered a form of speech recognition.
